Not
slothful
in business;
fervent
in spirit;
serving
the Lord;

Rejoicing
in hope;
patient
in tribulation;
continuing instant
in prayer;

(Touch
not;
taste
not;
handle
not;

For whoremongers,
for them that defile themselves with mankind,
for menstealers,
for liars,
for perjured persons,
and
if
there be
any
other thing
that is contrary to
sound
doctrine;

They
shall perish;
but
thou
remainest;
and
they all
shall wax old
as doth
a garment;

The fifth,
sardonyx;
